# Pockeet

Mobile receipt app: scan → parse → review → monthly clarity. EN/HE, RTL, calm premium UI.

## Required reading (before features)

- `docs/product/mvp-scope.md` — scope and loop
- `docs/ux/navigation.md` — routes
- `docs/design/tokens.md` + `docs/design/components.md`
- `docs/ai/cursor-rules.md` — full agent rules

## Hard rules

- Local-first capture; never block scan on network
- Semantic tokens only in features (no raw hex)
- Compose `src/components/ui` primitives; no feature-to-feature imports
- Money: `amountMinor` + `currencyCode`
- One chart max on Home; 2 tabs + FAB for MVP
- 44pt min touch targets; WCAG AA-oriented defaults
- RTL: logical start/end; amounts stay LTR

